Add VAT threshold tracking foundation (step 1/3)

- New `lib/vat.ts` module with pure helpers for VAT threshold logic:
  thresholds (41 250 EUR / 93 500 EUR HT), warning/danger ratios
  (70 % / 90 %), HT conversion, year-to-date helpers, projection of
  exceed date.
- 42 Vitest cases in `lib/vat.test.ts` covering boundaries, HT/TTC
  conversions, projection edge cases.
- Migration `20260515183000_add_vat_registered.sql` adds
  `is_vat_registered boolean default false` to `urssaf_profile`,
  mirrored in `supabase/schema.sql` and `lib/database.types.ts`.
- Enrich activity catalog with `vatCategory` so each activity maps
  to its applicable VAT seuil (services vs goods).
- New `VatRegistrationPicker` component (3-option tri-state) with a
  prominent personalized explainer panel showing the user's actual
  threshold and a concrete chiffre example.
- Onboarding gains an Etape 3 for the VAT question, persisted on
  profile insert. Account page gains a non-destructive VAT section
  (no reset on change, unlike activity / frequency).
